tags.name: Taxi-Brousse Station
tags.note: Brousses run daily, roughly from 5am to 5pm Monday through Satuday and limited on Sunday, leaving when full. The fare is 3,000 Ariary one way. Depending on the size, brousses fill to 18-25 people. The trip to Brickaville, the district capital, takes 1hr.
